'''Halyna Hutchins''' (Chiyukireniya: Галина Хатчінс, romanized: Halyna Hatchyns; née Androsovych, Chiyukireniya: Андросович; 1979 - October 21, 2021) anali wojambula kanema waku Ukraine komanso mtolankhani yemwe amagwira ntchito pamakanema opitilira 30, makanema apa TV ndi ma TV. Archnemy, Darlin ', ndi Blindfire. Pa Okutobala 21, 2021, adavulala kwambiri pachiwopsezo chowombera panthawi yopanga filimu yotchedwa Rust.<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Jacobs|first1=Julia|last2=Varenikova|first2=Maria|date=2021-10-22|title=A Cinematographer Killed on Set Is Recalled as Talented and Spirited|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/10/22/movies/halyna-hutchins-alec-baldwin-rust.html|access-date=2021-10-28|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>

== Cholowa ==
Mu Okutobala 2021, atamwalira Hutchins, aphunzitsi ndi abwenzi ake ku American Film Institute adakhazikitsa Halyna Hutchins Memorial Scholarship Fund yodzipereka kuthandiza maphunziro a akatswiri akanema achikazi. Mzimayi wa Hutchins a Matt Hutchins adavomereza ntchitoyi ndipo adapempha aliyense amene akufuna kulemekeza kukumbukira kwake kuti apereke ndalama ku thumba.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Halyna Hutchins Now Honorary ASC Member|url=https://theasc.com/news/halyna-hutchins-now-honorary-asc-member|website=[[American Society of Cinematographers]]|access-date=November 16, 2021|date=November 15, 2021}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Tizard|first=Will|date=November 16, 2021|title=Cinematographers Pay Tribute to Fallen Colleague Halyna Hutchins at EnergaCamerimage Film Festival|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/global/halyna-hutchins-camerimage-film-festival-1235113070/|access-date=November 16, 2021|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|language=en-US}}</ref>

Imfa ya Hutchins idauzira kuyitanitsa kusintha kwachitetezo chamfuti pamakanema amakanema. Alexi Hawley, wofalitsa wa ndondomeko ya apolisi aku America The Rookie, adatsimikizira kuti, pambuyo pa imfa ya Hutchins, mfuti zonse zamoyo pawonetsero ziyenera kusinthidwa ndi mfuti za Airsoft ndi CG kuwala. Eric Kripke, wowonetsa mndandanda wamasewera apamwamba a ku America a The Boys, nawonso adalumbira kuti aletsa zopanda kanthu ndi mfuti pawonetsero wake. Wopanga mafilimu a Bandar Albuliwi pambuyo pake adapereka lingaliro loletsa mfuti zenizeni pamaseti amakanema. Pempho lake loti apange "Lamulo la Halyna" linathandizidwa ndi wojambula komanso wotsogolera Olivia Wilde. Ojambula mafilimu oposa 200 adayitana kalata yotsegula kuti aletse zida zogwiritsira ntchito mafilimu.

Mu Novembala 2021, American Society of Cinematographers idalemekeza ntchito ya Hutchins ngati wojambula makanema pomupatsa umembala wake.<ref>{{Cite web|last=Welk|first=Brian|date=November 2, 2021|title=Cinematographers Group Calls for Ban of Functional Firearms on Sets After 'Rust' Tragedy|url=https://www.thewrap.com/cinematographers-guns-ban-film-sets-rust/|access-date=November 2, 2021|website=[[The Wrap]]}}</ref>

